text.tspan: Child mortality vs. share of children immunized against diphtheria,
Share of children (12-23 months) that are immunized against diphtheria, tetanus and pertussis (DTP3), versus the share of
newborns who die before reaching the age of five.
Data source: United Nations Inter-agency Group for Child Mortality Estimation (2025); WHO & UNICEF (2024)
